seo: 反弹Shell,在线生成器,代码生成,多种语言支持
seo_en: reverse shell, online generator, code generation, multi-language support
summary: 该插件用于生成多种编程语言的反弹Shell代码，帮助用户根据目标环境选择合适的代码实现远程控制或渗透测试。
summary_en: This plugin is used to generate reverse shell codes in various programming languages, helping users choose appropriate codes for remote control or penetration testing based on the target environment.
